com.chupacadabra.evolution.engine

Class DifferentialEvolutionEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chupacadabra.evolution.engine.DifferentialEvolutionEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DifferentialEvolutionState, DifferentialEvolutionReceiver

    public final class DifferentialEvolutionEngine
extends Object
implements DifferentialEvolutionReceiver
    The core differential evolution optimization engine.

    Basically this class strings together the pool creation, pool initialization, and generation iteration policies to create a fully-fledged optimizer.
